                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8052" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1253</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3287 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">稳稳的幸福：隆基“稳扎稳打”财务战略塑造之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Steady happiness: LONGi&#39;s &quot;steady and steady&quot; financial strategy shaping road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">冯文红，尤凌云，傅雅婷，徐泽宇，伍睿勤，罗金</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湘潭大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">隆基绿能科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色能源；稳健型财务战略；筹资战略；投资战略；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Green Energy; Sound Financial Strategy; Financing Strategy; Investment Strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在“碳中和”、“碳达峰”背景下，隆基见证了绿色清洁能源光伏产业的崛起和发展。隆基从半导体技术的积累到推动单晶硅片领域的技术革命，再从单晶硅重回主流到提出用太阳能科技改变地球生态，“稳扎稳打”成为全球最大的硅片、组件供应商。企业的发展离不开战略护航，财务战略更是应当与公司战略和目标相匹配。从隆基的筹资、投资、营运资本、股利分配四个方面与同类企业进行对比，我们认为隆基采用财务稳健型的战略与公司战略相辅相成。但是身处风云变幻的光伏市场，隆基稳健型的财务战略还适用吗？本案例通过选取绿色能源转型期中具有代表性的隆基，对其财务战略进行分析，让学生能站在动态的角度对公司的财务活动进行全局性、长期性和创造性的战略规划。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of &quot;carbon neutrality&quot; and &quot;carbon peaking&quot;, Longi has witnessed the rise and development of the green and clean energy photovoltaic industry. From the accumulation of semiconductor technology to the technological revolution in the field of monocrystalline silicon wafers, and from the return of monocrystalline silicon to the mainstream to the proposal of changing the ecology of the earth with solar technology, Longi has become the world&#39;s largest supplier of silicon wafers and modules &quot;steadily and steadily&quot;. The development of a company cannot be separated from its strategy, and the financial strategy should match the company&#39;s strategy and objectives. Comparing Longi&#39;s fund raising, investment, working capital and dividend distribution with similar companies, we believe that Longi&#39;s financially prudent strategy complements the company&#39;s strategy. But in a volatile photovoltaic market, can LONGi&#39;s prudent financial strategy make it through the turbulence? This case study analyses the financial strategy of Longi, a representative example of the green energy transition, to enable students to take a dynamic perspective on the company&#39;s financial activities and to plan strategically in a holistic, long-term and creative manner.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司财务战略》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务战略类型；财务战略内容；财务战略制定的影响因素；</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
